name: Tillamook Strawberry
description: Tillamook Strawberry is a mash-up between Alphakronik Genes and Dark Horse Genetics for AKG’s Collaboration Series. Described by the breeder as the “diesel lover’s dream,” Tillamook Strawberry smells like a gas station in a strawberry field. The strain’s foliage is deep green with tight buds and the effects are bright yet soothing, promoting focus and relaxation. Utilize Tillamook Strawberry to improve your mood and counter depression and anxiety.

highlightedReviews.text: really hope to see some pics and hesr some peoples reviews. it grows kinda like some north lights and is fast vegging and close internodes on most phenos beautiful plant smells amazing even in veg. just put in budding with some NL and Afgan and BD should be interesting. im very excited about this i know not to man people grow it or it would be all over leafly but once budding is over ill add pic. i just put motherd in after i took 4 clones from 7 plants and finding out male or female and will post again when i have data from each plant and ill give all the info i can but so far im very impressed. i have resd taht it takes up to 65 days to flower but it took 3 weeks and it was ready for flowering im going to grow it in different sized pots and see which is tje best and do as many test i can to get as much data out there for everyone else growing it. im gonan try it outdoors in oregon and see how it does out here. ill post each week and hopefullt it helps anyone that is seeking answers cause there is very little info on this strain. i also have a strain called love lace its a cbd strain and very little info on it if anyone has info on either of these i would like to share anything i can and get as much info as i can. also this strian is a very powerful strain up to 26.7 and i believe i can get that and if everything goes right maybe more im gonna cross is with every strain i have including blue dream and NL and make the best meds i can.

Very smooth texture. Cant taste the sweet that it describes. But it burns really nice. I got mega sleepy on it. My mom said my eyes were strawberry red. But my eyes went heavy. Then i went down for the count. All in all. A good weed for me to use before bed.
